entry.title: BIP-85 Champion Unreachable? Please weigh in.
entry.summary: Ethan Kosakovsky, the original author referenced in the initiative, has not shown any activity on GitHub since 2021. His profile can be reviewed [here](https://github.com/ethankosakovsky). This information highlights a possible gap or pause in contributions from Ethan to the GitHub community, which could be relevant for various reasons including but not limited to project continuation, updates, or collaborations.
